                                    "val" : {"type" : "LSString", "value" : "She digs a hand into her chest (OOS), grits her teeth and wrenches - pulls out the heart. \r\n\r\nKarlach throws her heart aside as her flames lose their orange hue, and take on the same colouring as the Netherbain's magic.\r\n\r\nGreasy smile. "}
